---
title: Herbed Honey & Sesame-Coated Beef with Roast Veggie Israeli Couscous & Crumbly Cheese
description: Cook a succulent beef strips lightly coated in a sesame crumb for extra 'wow' factor. With honey, herbs, hearty Israeli couscous and roasted veggies, this dinner has the lot and is sure to leave you feeling satisfied with every delicious mouthful.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
